  "description": "This game is actually a lot like chess!  It’s a games designed to simulate pitched battles in the Ancient world. There is a set of armies available from the earliest times until the fall of the Western Roman Empire, in 475 A.D.<br><br>You can design the terrain and/or units, set-up each side’s troops and then it's just on to the battle. You are doing nothing but fighting the battle you created.<br><br>There are also some pre-designed scenarios and maps for your enjoyment.\n",
